Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.23,0:00:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗发现了新的女王候补啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.40,0:00:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经在很近的地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.57,0:00:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得去见见她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.72,0:02:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.81,0:02:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况不妙暂且逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.85,0:02:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.62,0:02:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.25,0:02:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯还好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.83,0:03:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个贵族居然只为了打倒尚文就解除魔物的封印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.30,0:03:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.13,0:03:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.47,0:03:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉芙塔莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.64,0:03:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么之后该
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.60,0:03:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会察觉我们在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.61,0:03:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶要是现在冲过来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.61,0:03:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.28,0:03:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小菲洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.03,0:03:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.12,0:03:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算在这里战斗吗这里可是城市中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.21,0:03:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道先把它引城外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.46,0:03:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要怎么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.43,0:03:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.72,0:03:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.77,0:04:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看小菲洛的肚子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.65,0:04:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那只魔物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.52,0:04:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道它在追赶的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.11,0:04:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.61,0:04:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么如果顺利的话就能把它引到城外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.03,0:04:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.99,0:04:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有问题我会带着这些孩子逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.29,0:04:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.12,0:04:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉芙塔莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.04,0:04:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说拉芙塔莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.67,0:04:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是盾之勇者大人的同伴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.89,0:04:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你得走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.06,0:04:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.52,0:04:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.19,0:04:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.32,0:04:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请放心我先去和他们会合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.03,0:04:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.07,0:04:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,范大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.91,0:05:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.42,0:05:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.92,0:05:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.05,0:05:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.22,0:05:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.76,0:05:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.31,0:05:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能再见面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.44,0:05:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.86,0:05:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.69,0:05:30.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.79,0:05:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.67,0:05:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛往那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.46,0:05:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.26,0:06:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是在追小菲洛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.85,0:06:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉那个手环
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.36,0:06:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你的东西随你处置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.71,0:06:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要跑多远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.54,0:06:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽可能远离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.39,0:06:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快离开森林了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.15,0:06:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在这里的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.53,0:07:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.29,0:07:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时可以战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.08,0:07:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.34,0:07:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵气盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.94,0:07:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中级水刃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.53,0:07:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砍不进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.33,0:07:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然行动迟钝但是防御太高了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.50,0:07:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人我要落脚点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.17,0:07:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵气盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.51,0:08:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二面盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.93,0:08:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.85,0:08:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.33,0:08:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.25,0:08:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.16,0:08:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.25,0:08:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的体力有限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.88,0:08:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只能使用愤怒之盾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.51,0:08:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.59,0:08:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.80,0:08:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文附近的情况很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.22,0:08:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是魔法雾?相当高位的结界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.94,0:08:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结界?我们被关起来了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.45,0:09:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有东西来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.29,0:09:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛鸟?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.51,0:09:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟发生了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.69,0:09:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.03,0:09:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你别太依赖那股力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.66,0:09:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.24,0:10:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是菲洛鸟女王?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.62,0:10:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.54,0:10:35.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们退后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.58,0:10:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来龙帝的碎片不适合你的体质使你巨大化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.09,0:10:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果马上将碎片交给我我不会杀掉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.05,0:10:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻滚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.72,0:10:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.60,0:10:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.28,0:11:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力道太弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.46,0:11:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽快解决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.27,0:11:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是盾之勇者大人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.74,0:11:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有很多话想对你说这副模样太失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.95,0:11:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.38,0:12:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么先自我介绍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.09,0:12:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是统治全世界菲洛鸟的女王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.10,0:12:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲托莉亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.90,0:12:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲托莉亚?那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.27,0:12:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.94,0:12:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯据说是很久以前被召唤来的勇者所养育的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.07,0:12:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说中的菲洛鸟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.78,0:12:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.53,0:12:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说这家伙继承了那名字吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.00,0:12:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前起叫菲托莉亚的就只有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.58,0:12:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后菲洛也能变得那么大吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.21,0:12:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得那么大我养不起扔掉你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.59,0:12:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成长到这么大需要花费一般菲洛鸟繁殖数十代的时间放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.77,0:13:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说她活了很久吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.06,0:13:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是盾之勇者大人一行请自我介绍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.40,0:13:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是岩谷尚文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.07,0:13:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫拉芙塔莉雅请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.66,0:13:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛叫菲洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.91,0:13:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前我们见过呢感谢你当时的帮助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.25,0:13:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我叫梅尔蒂·梅洛马格请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.42,0:13:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你就是梅尔炭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.71,0:13:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅尔炭?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.51,0:13:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们见过吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.34,0:13:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯从外交地回到王都途中认识的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.60,0:13:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前也做过类似的事情吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.18,0:13:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么感谢你打倒了那只魔物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.52,0:13:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你找我们有什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.19,0:13:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先我要听听前因后果但这里不适合慢慢交谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.53,0:13:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带路这边请
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.53,0:14:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在此之前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.24,0:14:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜欢看到与龙有关的东西在四圣勇者装备里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.08,0:14:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是用来强化盾牌的重要材料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.25,0:14:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且盾牌上有不祥的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.63,0:14:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诅咒的力量的确强大但是代价也很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.76,0:14:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.47,0:14:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以控制没有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.22,0:14:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天会控制不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.64,0:14:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不管龙的材料还是愤怒之盾都是我活下去所必须的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.27,0:14:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗随便你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.78,0:14:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.08,0:14:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备完了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.87,0:14:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯剩下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.12,0:14:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会命令眷属带过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.33,0:14:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.17,0:14:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巫上马车我想在那边问你很多问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.63,0:14:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.56,0:15:06.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.27,0:15:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然可以瞬间移动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.69,0:15:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好历害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.19,0:15:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遗迹吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.15,0:15:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有历史感呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.32,0:15:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.32,0:15:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是最初的勇者所守护的国家的遗迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.20,0:15:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得好模糊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.62,0:15:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是菲托莉亚出生前就存在的地方我姑且在管理这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.87,0:15:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是菲洛鸟的圣域吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.42,0:15:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错其实不应该带太多人类来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.51,0:15:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那大概比较安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.01,0:15:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之你们慢慢休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.10,0:15:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.02,0:15:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.57,0:15:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一天好辛苦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.32,0:16:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基尔他们没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.24,0:16:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有范和亚人们跟着没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.78,0:16:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.79,0:16:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先来吃饭吧大家都肚子饿了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.09,0:16:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.97,0:16:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这这就有点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.81,0:16:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.69,0:16:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.98,0:16:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.56,0:16:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.86,0:16:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像姐妹一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.90,0:16:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯粗犷的进食方式一模一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.20,0:16:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个尚文大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.16,0:16:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了我帮你们做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.54,0:16:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿大锅和食材来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.26,0:17:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我还要做给它们吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.14,0:17:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛没有多的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.65,0:17:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道剛刚好我有话想说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.95,0:17:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道遭到封印的魔物为什么会被释放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.49,0:17:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为你了解情况才会来救我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.87,0:17:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲托莉亚会来是因为收到了发现新女王候补的报告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.38,0:17:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王候补菲洛吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.13,0:17:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能问个问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.93,0:17:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.55,0:17:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲洛的成长方式为什么和其他菲洛鸟完全不同?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.06,0:17:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.06,0:17:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是勇者养育的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.98,0:18:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我为什么封印被解开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.91,0:18:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.45,0:18:22.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了终末的浪潮已经临近却还在进行愚蠢斗争的四圣勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.67,0:18:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他们不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.26,0:18:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道盾之勇者被排斥亚人的国家厌恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.93,0:18:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你应该能明白吧所以我们才要跨越国境…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.72,0:18:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不能解决问题去面对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.19,0:18:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管人类和亚人的争端再激烈也不允许勇者内讧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.74,0:18:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四圣勇者不知道沙漏吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.25,0:19:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙刻沙漏吗这我倒是知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.50,0:19:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么不参加全世界的浪潮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.34,0:19:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.05,0:19:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在梅洛马格之外的各地也有浪潮吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.76,0:19:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本应该每个国家召唤一位四圣勇者来应对浪潮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.10,0:19:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我是第一次听说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.81,0:19:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲托莉亚尽到了自己的职责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.40,0:19:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是四圣勇者却不去应对其他地方的浪潮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.11,0:19:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是最近才知道其他国家也有沙漏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.03,0:19:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实说我不在乎人类变得怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.95,0:19:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲托莉亚只是在按照养育自己的勇者的愿望在战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.25,0:19:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者的愿望?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.63,0:19:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲托莉亚的职责是保护世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.50,0:19:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓人类的下场却要拯救世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.51,0:19:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只靠菲托莉亚不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.09,0:19:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有勇者在保护不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.55,0:19:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你比我们要强多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.35,0:20:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.19,0:20:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是总有一天我会拯救不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.28,0:20:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才需要勇者吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.49,0:20:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.67,0:20:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.46,0:20:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.39,0:20:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来三勇教的确隐瞒了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.94,0:20:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然和尚文说的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.95,0:20:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,书库吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.87,0:20:58.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调查一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.29,0:21:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此一举
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.96,0:21:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是要我与他们和解?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.63,0:21:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者们必须齐心协力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.76,0:21:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是守护世界的必要条件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.43,0:21:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.85,0:21:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙和国家打算排挤我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.60,0:21:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说了一些情况但是勇者之间不能产生争斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.02,0:21:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真坚持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.19,0:21:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这点不能妥协
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.03,0:21:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们根本不打算和我好好相处没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.45,0:21:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.87,0:21:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗那就没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.08,0:21:53.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这已经是很久以前的事连记忆都有些模糊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.80,0:21:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我只记得这样做才是正确的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.18,0:22:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明浪潮就已经很难对付了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.43,0:22:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然勇者之间要互相争斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.02,0:22:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么为了世界我要杀掉四圣勇者
